---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import ProjectCta from '../components/ProjectCta.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Mineral Processing Equipment Manufacturing & Delivery"
  description="Equipment coordination, production review, quality checks, packing and export delivery from our manufacturing base and supply network in China."
>
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Manufacturing & Delivery' }]} />
      <span class="eyebrow">Jiangxi manufacturing base</span>
      <h1>Manufacturing & Delivery</h1>
      <p>
        The flowsheet defines the equipment duty. We then coordinate manufacturing, interfaces,
        checks, documentation, packing and export delivery around that duty.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div><span class="eyebrow">One accountable route</span><h2>Control the interfaces.</h2></div>
        <p>
          Many plant problems occur between machines: mismatched discharge heights, uncontrolled
          pumps, missing chutes, unsuitable motors or undocumented recirculating streams.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <article class="surface-card"><h3>Manufacturing review</h3><p>Confirm duty, materials, drives, interfaces and the approved technical scope before production.</p></article>
        <article class="surface-card"><h3>Quality checks</h3><p>Record agreed inspection points, dimensions, components and visible test conditions before packing.</p></article>
        <article class="surface-card"><h3>Packing & shipment</h3><p>Coordinate packing lists, container planning, markings and export documents with the delivery scope.</p></article>
      </div>
      <div class="authorization-note">
        <strong>Production wording policy</strong>
        <p>
          This site currently uses “manufacturing base and supply network.” Change public wording to
          “our factory” only after written authorization covers brand use, images, customer visits,
          warranty and delivery responsibility.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <ProjectCta />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .authorization-note {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 24px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    background: var(--paper-deep);
  }

  .authorization-note strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .authorization-note p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 650px) {
    .authorization-note {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
